2020年10月31日，位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[魁北克市|魁北克市]][[魁北克老城|老城]]的[[魁北克省议会大厦|省議會大廈]]附近發生'''持刀襲擊事件'''，共造成兩人死亡，五人受傷。死者分別為61歲的女子和56歲男子<ref>{{cite web |last1=Duval |first1=Alexandre |title=L'identité des victimes de l'attaque dans le Vieux-Québec dévoilée |url=https://ici.radio-canada.ca/nouvelle/1746133/identite-victimes-attaque-vieux-quebec-arme-blanche |website=[[Radio_Canada|Radio Canada]] |accessdate=1 November 2020 |language=fr |date=1 November 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101181133/https://ici.radio-canada.ca/nouvelle/1746133/identite-victimes-attaque-vieux-quebec-arme-blanche |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC">{{Cite news|date=2020-11-01|title=Quebec stabbing: Two dead after attack by man in medieval clothes|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-54766208|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107043413/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-54766208|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Suspect in custody after 2 killed, 5 injured in Quebec City stabbings: police|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/7435389/quebec-city-stabbing/|access-date=2020-11-01|website=Global News|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101113606/https://globalnews.ca/news/7435389/quebec-city-stabbing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Nov 1|first=AP / Updated:|last2=2020|last3=Ist|first3=13:21|title=Quebec Stabbings: Police arrest suspect after stabbings in Quebec City kills 2 {{!}} World News - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/police-arrest-suspect-after-stabbings-in-quebec-city-kills-2/articleshow/78979280.cms|access-date=2020-11-01|website=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101064448/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/police-arrest-suspect-after-stabbings-in-quebec-city-kills-2/articleshow/78979280.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>，兇嫌已被逮捕。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Staff|first=Scroll|title=Canada: Two dead, five injured in Quebec stabbing attack, suspect arrested|url=https://scroll.in/latest/977369/canada-two-dead-five-injured-in-quebec-stabbing-attack-suspect-arrested|access-date=2020-11-01|website=Scroll.in|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101070310/https://scroll.in/latest/977369/canada-two-dead-five-injured-in-quebec-stabbing-attack-suspect-arrested|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=2 Dead, 5 Injured In Stabbing Incident In Quebec; Suspect Arrested|url=https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/multiple-people-injured-in-stabbing-incident-in-canadas-quebec-suspect-arrested-says-police-news-agency-afp-2318863|access-date=2020-11-01|website=NDTV.com|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101063216/https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/multiple-people-injured-in-stabbing-incident-in-canadas-quebec-suspect-arrested-says-police-news-agency-afp-2318863|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事發過程 ==
報導稱施襲者身穿“中世紀服裝”，<ref>{{Cite news|last=Press|first=The Associated|date=2020-11-01|title=Man in medieval clothing leaves 'multiple victims' in Quebec City stabbing attack|language=en-GB|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/01/man-in-medieval-clothing-leaves-multiple-victims-in-quebec-city-stabbing-attack|access-date=2020-11-01|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208193500/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/01/man-in-medieval-clothing-leaves-multiple-victims-in-quebec-city-stabbing-attack|dead-url=no}}</ref>因案發當晚為[[萬聖節|萬聖節]]，因此推測該套服裝可能與萬聖節裝扮有關。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Ramzy|first=Austin|date=2020-11-01|title=2 Killed in Halloween Stabbing Spree in Quebec City|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/01/world/canada/quebec-city-stabbing-deaths-halloween-medieval-costume.html|access-date=2020-11-01|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104225853/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/01/world/canada/quebec-city-stabbing-deaths-halloween-medieval-costume.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>襲擊發生在魁北克省议会大厦附近，該建築為[[魁北克國民議會|魁北克國民議會]]的會議地點。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Two dead, five injured in Quebec City stabbing; police arrest lone suspect|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/canada/article-police-hunt-for-suspect-in-medieval-garb-after-stabbings-in-quebec/|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101053825/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/canada/article-police-hunt-for-suspect-in-medieval-garb-after-stabbings-in-quebec/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{le|魁北克省警方|Sûreté du Québec}}稱受傷的五人已經被送往當地醫院接受治療。<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-11-01|title=Quebec City police arrest suspect after stabbings leave 2 dead|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/quebec-city-police-stabbings-1.5785401|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123050248/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/quebec-city-police-stabbings-1.5785401|archive-date=2021-01-23|access-date=|website=CBC News|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Police Report|url=https://twitter.com/SPVQ_police/status/1322773809640935424?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1322773809640935424%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fmontreal%2Fquebec-city-police-stabbings-1.5785401|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208193532/https://twitter.com/SPVQ_police/status/1322773809640935424?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1322773809640935424%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fmontreal%2Fquebec-city-police-stabbings-1.5785401|archive-date=2020-12-08|access-date=2020-11-01|website=Twitter|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>警方表示，兇手在5年前曾計劃使用此次事件的類似手法襲擊醫生<ref name="soleil">{{cite web |last1=Desmeules |first1=Judith |title=Tuerie dans le Vieux-Québec: les victimes choisies au hasard |url=https://www.lesoleil.com/actualite/justice-et-faits-divers/tuerie-dans-le-vieux-quebec-les-victimes-choisies-au-hasard-video-3df62593ea7fc234ad92391ceb30b6e6 |website=[[Le_Soleil|Le Soleil]] |accessdate=1 November 2020 |language=fr |date=1 November 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102233457/https://www.lesoleil.com/actualite/justice-et-faits-divers/tuerie-dans-le-vieux-quebec-les-victimes-choisies-au-hasard-video-3df62593ea7fc234ad92391ceb30b6e6 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Two dead, five injured in Quebec City stabbing; police arrest lone suspect|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/canada/article-police-hunt-for-suspect-in-medieval-garb-after-stabbings-in-quebec/|last=Tu Thanh|first=Ha|newspaper=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|date=1 November 2020|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101053825/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/canada/article-police-hunt-for-suspect-in-medieval-garb-after-stabbings-in-quebec/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

